variables.name: STATE_EARLY
variables.comment: * The device has sent out a dialog starting event and is awaiting a confirmation.

variables.name: STATE_CONFIRMED
variables.comment: * The device has received a 2XX response to the early dialog.

variables.name: STATE_CLOSED
variables.comment:
* The device has received either a 3XX+ response to a pending dialog request or a BYE
     * request has been sent on this dialog.
